the chinese consulate general in karachi confirmed on the $number that three chinese engineers and a pakistani driver were killed in an attack yesterday in the southwestern pakistani province of balochistan . 
upon learning the news late last night , chinese state president hu jintao showed deep concern for the safety of chinese engineering and technical personnel in pakistan . 
he instructed the foreign ministry , the chinese embassy and consulate in pakistan to require pakistan to catch the murderers , ensure the safety of chinese personnel in pakistan , and properly handle the aftermath arising from the deaths of the victims . 
