in accordance with president hu jintao 's instruction , foreign minster li zhaoxing made an urgent call to pakistani foreign minister kasuri before dawn today . 
the chinese embassy and consulate in pakistan immediately activated the emergency mechanism , and relevant personnel have already rushed to the scene . 
