in addition , according to the latest information from the chinese consulate general in karachi , the remains of the three chinese were transported to karachi early this morning and will be shipped back to china by charter plane in a few days . 
after the attack , the chinese consulate general in karachi immediately dispatched a three - person task force to the scene and transported the remains of the three chinese engineers to be placed in a hospital in karachi . 
in the meantime , $number chinese personnel working in the same place with these people have been called back to karachi . at present they are emotionally stabilized . 
the attack took place in a town called hub in southeast quetta . 
on the afternoon of that day , six chinese engineers who worked in a local cement factory were riding in a car leaving the construction site for their residence when an unidentified criminal on a motorcycle stopped them . 
the criminal used a submachine gun to fire a barrage of shots , and three engineers died unfortunately . 
following the attack , a tribal militant organization called " the balochistan liberation army " claimed responsibility for the incident . 
the pakistani foreign ministry issued a statement that night strongly condemning the attack and calling it an act of terrorism . 
the three chinese who died in the attack were long hongbao , wei jianping , and zhao bin , technical staff from the hefei cement research and design institute in anhui owned by the china national building material group corporation . 
chinese foreign ministry spokesman qin gang said today that chinese government leaders showed deep concern over the incident of the chinese engineering and technical personnel attacked in pakistan and required the pakistani side to ensure the safety of chinese personnel in pakistan and to promptly catch the murderers . 
qin gang said that chinese ambassador to pakistan zhang chunxiang has reported the relevant information and made representations to the pakistani government and military officials . 
pakistan strongly condemned the barbarous and cruel incident and expressed condolences on the death of the chinese personnel , vowing to catch the murderers and fully cooperate with the chinese side in dealing with the incident . 
the foreign ministry is currently coordinating with relevant departments to arrange for the remains of the victims to be shipped back to china as soon as possible . 
a task force dealing with the aftermath formed by the cnbm hefei cement research and design institute in anhui , the institution that sent the victims , left beijing this morning for pakistan . 
