the attack happened in the town of hub , southeast of quetta . 
on that day , six chinese engineers who worked at a local cement factory were in a car returning to their residences from their work site . their car was suddenly stopped by some unidentified gunmen on motorcycles . 
the gunmen opened fire with assault rifles , killing three engineers . 
after the attack , a tribal militant group named the baloch liberation army claimed responsibility for the shooting . 
