who will win the championship at last ? 
based on an analysis of actual strengths , although the taishan team has a great hope of seizing the championship , it has no full certainty of success . 
$number , the time for new team members to adapt to each other is short . 
the taishan team had nothing new last year . 
the taishan team introduced li leilei and wang liang , the two members from the national team , this year . soon after that , it will also add two members to the team from foreign teams , and its actual strength should be seen as increased , not reduced . 
