when they return to the football club , the league matches will start right away , 
so , the issue of adapting to each other is the biggest issue the taishan team is facing . 
i think that those members from the national team can be substitute players for $number several rounds of games in the league matches . 
firstly , they can be trained to adapt to the team in matches ; 
secondly , those national team members who have played two group matches can have a rest . 
after several rounds of matches , their edge would be honed , and it won 't be too late for them to participate . 
$number , its defense has hidden problems . 
