welcome everybody to the china news programs . 
china 's consulate - general in karachi confirmed on the $number that three chinese engineers and one pakistani driver died yesterday in an attack in balochistan in southwest pakistan . 
after learning of the incident late last night , chinese president hu jintao was deeply concerned for the safety of china 's engineers and technicians in pakistan . 
he instructed the ministry of foreign affairs and the chinese embassy in pakistan to pressure the pakistani authorities to apprehend the assailants , ensure the safety of the chinese personnel in pakistan and appropriately handle arrangements related to those who were killed . 
hu jintao also expressed profound sorrow for the unfortunate deaths of the chinese personnel and expressed his sincere condolences to their families . 
early this morning , as instructed by president hu jintao , foreign minister li zhaoxing had an urgent phone conversation with pakistan minister of foreign affairs kasuri . 
the chinese embassy in pakistan immediately activated its emergency mechanism and relevant personnel rushed to the scene . 
premier wen jiabao also issued instructions on ensuring the safety of chinese personnel , properly handling the necessary arrangements and requiring pakistani authorities to apprehend the killers . 
also , according to the latest news from the chinese consulate - general in karachi , the bodies of the three chinese were transported to karachi early this morning to be repatriated in a special plane within a few days . 
following the attack , the chinese consulate - general in karachi quickly sent a three - member team to the scene to transport the bodies of the three chinese engineers to a hospital in karachi for storage . 
at the same time , more than ten chinese personnel working at the same worksite as the victims were also evacuated to karachi . their emotions are currently stable . 
the attack occurred in a town called hub in the southeast of gwador . 
that afternoon , six chinese engineers working in a local cement plant were returning from the worksite to their base in a car when they were cut off by an unidentified assailant on a motorcycle . 
the assailants sprayed them with machine - gun fire , killing three of the engineers . 
after the attack , a armed tribal group called the " balochistan liberation army " claimed responsibility . 
the pakistani ministry of foreign affairs issued a statement that evening strongly condemning the attack and calling it a terrorist act . 
the three chinese killed in the attack are long hongbao , wei jianping and zhao bin , all technicians with the anhui hefei cement industrial design and research institute under the china national building materials group corporation . 
chinese foreign ministry spokesman qin gang said today that china 's leaders were deeply concerned by the attack on chinese engineers and technicians in pakistan and were asking pakistani authorities to ensure the safety of chinese personnel in pakistan and apprehend the assailants as soon as possible . 
qin gang said that chinese ambassador to pakistan zhang chunxiang had communicated with pakistan 's state and military leaders on the situation and had discussed the matter with them . 
pakistan strongly condemned this brutal and cruel incident , expressed its condolences for the deaths of the chinese employees and said it would do its utmost to apprehend the assailants and work with the chinese in dealing with the matter . 
the ministry of foreign affairs is coordinating with related departments to expedite repatriation of the victims ' bodies . 
a tragedy response team from the victims ' dispatching unit , anhui hefei cement industrial design and research institute under the china national building materials group corporation , left beijing this morning for pakistan . 
china 's ministry of commerce also set up an emergency response team following the incident . 
assistant minister of commerce chen jian said that if it cannot be assured that activity can be carried out in security , the cement plant project will not resume work . 
only when the security of construction personnel is assured can work be continued . 
after the ( emergency ) group was set up , we immediately ... eh ... instructed our field personnel to go to the scene and complete an investigation of local conditions . 
at the same time , here in china we verified the identity of the victims as quickly as possible . 
chen jian said that the ministry of commerce would closely follow the handling of the incident and actively coordinate the relevant units in the handling of the necessary arrangements . 
if security cannot be assured for the time being , we will require chinese enterprises to suspend work . 
work will resume only when security is effectively assured . 
