beijing , $date ( xinhua ) ( reporter : li xing ) in a bid to increase china 's international competitiveness , vigorously promote sustainable development , and realize breakthroughs in key areas , the national guideline on medium - and long - term programs for science and technology development ( $number ) published by the state council on the $number lays out four areas of major scientific research . 
