the guideline says protein science is a peak of the life sciences that has developed countries energetically vying with each other . 
in the next $number years , china will give top priority to the study of the transcriptomics of major biological systems , proteomics , metabolomics , structural biology , protein 's biological capabilities and other interactions , biology and system biology for protein - related calculations , methodology for protein research and basic research for related applications . 
the guideline also said that research into the control of quanta was clearly foresighted and that in $number years it may have imponderable impact on mankind 's social and economic development . 
