according to the guidelines , $date china will focus its research on stem cell proliferation , division and control ; the occurrence , maturation and fertilization of reproductive cells ; the decline of human reproductive capabilities and the mechanism for degenerative illnesses ; and the safety and principles of assisted reproduction and stem cell technology . 
