the plan defines the policies for voluntary aids consultation and testing in hebei : testing for aids antibodies and consultation shall be free ; testing for aids antibodies and consultation shall be voluntary and based on informed consent ; testing for aids antibodies and consultation shall be confidential and no judgment shall be made of the consultation - seeker 's related behavior ; the legal rights and benefits of those infected with the aids virus and those sick with aids shall be p 
