lodi gyaltsen gyari said in washington that he hopes that the chinese government will truly protect tibet 's unique culture and traditions . 
it is expected that during his visit to the us next week the dalai lama will discuss the tibet issue with president bush in the hope that bush will press the chinese government to give tibet genuine autonomy . 
in $date of this year , envoys of the dalai lama 's met with beijing 's officials in berne for their $number direct contact . 
" genuine autonomy " 
